Definition: [ἀναντίῤῥητος] from {{g1}} (as a negative particle) and a presumed derivative of a compound of {{g473}} and {{g4483}}; indisputable
[ἀναντιῤῥήτως] adverb from {{g368}}; promptly
[ἀναλύω] from {{g303}} and {{g3089}}; to break up, i.e. depart (literally or figuratively)
[ἀναμάρτητος] from {{g1}} (as a negative particle) and a presumed derivative of {{g264}}; sinless
[ἀναμένω] from {{g303}} and {{g3306}}; to await
[ἀναμιμνήσκω] from {{g303}} and {{g3403}}; to remind; (reflexively) to recollect
[ἀνάμνησις] from {{g363}}; recollection
[ἀνανεόω] from {{g303}} and a derivative of {{g3501}}; to renovate, i.e. reform
[ἀνανήφω] from {{g303}} and {{g3525}}; to become sober again, i.e. (figuratively) regain (one's) senses
[Ἀνανίας] of Hebrew origin ({{h2608}}); Ananias, the name of three Israelites
[ἀνατολή] from {{g393}}; a rising of light, i.e. dawn (figuratively); by implication, the east (also in plural)
[ἀνατίθεμαι] from {{g303}} and the middle voice of {{g5087}}; to set forth (for oneself), i.e propound
[ἀνατρέφω] from {{g303}} and {{g5142}}; to rear (physically or mentally)
[ἀνατρέπω] from {{g303}} and the base of {{g5157}}; to overturn (figuratively)
[ἀναστροφή] from {{g390}}; behavior
[ἀναστρέφω] from {{g303}} and {{g4762}}; to overturn; also to return; by implication, to busy oneself, i.e. remain, live
[ἀνατέλλω] from {{g303}} and the base of {{g5056}}; to (cause to) arise
[ἀνατάσσομαι] from {{g303}} and the middle voice of {{g5021}}; to arrange
[ἀναφέρω] from {{g303}} and {{g5342}}; to take up (literally or figuratively)
[ἀναφαίνω] from {{g303}} and {{g5316}}; to show, i.e. (reflexively) appear, or (passively) to have pointed out
[ἀναπολόγητος] from {{g1}} (as a negative particle) and a presumed derivative of {{g626}}; indefensible
[ἀναπληρόω] from {{g303}} and {{g4137}}; to complete; by implication, to occupy, supply; figuratively, to accomplish (by coincidence ot obedience)
[ἀναπαύω] from {{g303}} and {{g3973}}; (reflexively) to repose (literally or figuratively (be exempt), remain); by implication, to refresh
[ἀνάπαυσις] from {{g373}}; intermission; by implication, recreation
[ἀναξίως] adverb from {{g370}}; irreverently
[ἀνάξιος] from {{g1}} (as a negative particle) and {{g514}}; unfit
[ἀναπίπτω] from {{g303}} and {{g4098}}; to fall back, i.e. lie down, lean back
[ἀνάπηρος] from {{g303}} (in the sense of intensity) and πῆρος (maimed); crippled
[ἀναπέμπω] from {{g303}} and {{g3992}}; to send up or back
[ἀναπείθω] from {{g303}} and {{g3982}}; to incite
[ἀναφωνέω] from {{g303}} and {{g5455}}; to exclaim
[ἀνακεφαλαίομαι] from {{g303}} and {{g2775}} (in its original sense); to sum up
[ἀνακλίνω] from {{g303}} and {{g2827}}; to lean back
[ἀνακάμπτω] from {{g303}} and {{g2578}}; to turn back
[ἀνακεῖμαι] from {{g303}} and {{g2749}}; to recline (as a corpse or at a meal)
[ἀνακαίνωσις] from {{g341}}; renovation
[ἀνακαλύπτω] from {{g303}} (in the sense of reversal) and {{g2572}}; to unveil
[ἀνακαινίζω] from {{g303}} and a derivative of {{g2537}}; to restore
[ἀνακαινόω] from {{g303}} and a derivative of {{g2537}}; to renovate
[ἀνακόπτω] from {{g303}} and {{g2875}}; to beat back, i.e. check
[ἀνακράζω] from {{g303}} and {{g2896}}; to scream up (aloud)
[ἀνάκρισις] from {{g350}}; a (judicial) investigation
[ἀνακρίνω] from {{g303}} and {{g2919}}; properly, to scrutinize, i.e. (by implication) investigate, interrogate, determine
[ἀναλαμβάνω] from {{g303}} and {{g2983}}; to take up
[ἀνακύπτω] from {{g303}} (in the sense of reversal) and {{g2955}}; to unbend, i.e. rise; figuratively, be elated
[ἀναλίσκω] from {{g303}} and a form of the alternate of {{g138}}; properly, to use up, i.e. destroy
[ἀνάληψις] from {{g353}}; ascension
[ἀναλογίζομαι] middle voice from {{g356}}; to estimate, i.e. (figuratively) contemplate
[ἀναλογία] from a compound of {{g303}} and {{g3056}}; proportion
[ἀνάλυσις] from {{g360}}; departure
[ἄναλος] from {{g1}} (as a negative particle) and {{g251}}; saltless, i.e. insipid
[ἀναδέχομαι] from {{g303}} and {{g1209}}; to entertain (as a guest)
[ἀναδίδωμι] from {{g303}} and {{g1325}}; to hand over
[ἀναζάω] from {{g303}} and {{g2198}}; to recover life (literally or figuratively)
[ἀναζητέω] from {{g303}} and {{g2212}}; to search out
[ἀνάγνωσις] from {{g314}}; (the act of) reading
[ἀνάγω] from {{g303}} and {{g71}}; to lead up; by extension to bring out; specially, to sail away
[ἀναδείκνυμι] from {{g303}} and {{g1166}}; to exhibit, i.e. (by implication) to indicate, appoint
[ἀνάδειξις] from {{g322}}; (the act of) exhibition
[ἀναζώννυμι] from {{g303}} and {{g2224}}; to gird afresh
[ἀναζωπυρέω] from {{g303}} and a compound of the base of {{g2226}} and {{g4442}}; to re-enkindle
[ἀναιρέω] from {{g303}} and (the active of) {{g138}}; to take up, i.e. adopt; by implication, to take away (violently), i.e. abolish, murder
[ἀναίρεσις] from {{g337}}; (the act of) killing
[ἀναίδεια] from a compound of {{g1}} (as a negative particle (compare {{g427}})) and {{g127}}; impudence, i.e. (by implication) importunity
[ἀνάθημα] from {{g394}} (like {{g331}}, but in a good sense); a votive offering
[ἀναθεωρέω] from {{g303}} and {{g2334}}; to look again (i.e. attentively) at (literally or figuratively)
[ἀναθεματίζω] from {{g331}}; to declare or vow under penalty of execration
[ἀνάθεμα] from {{g394}}; a (religious) ban or (concretely) excommunicated (thing or person)
[ἀναθάλλω] from {{g303}} and θάλλω (to flourish); to revive
[ἀνακαθίζω] from {{g303}} and {{g2523}}; properly, to set up, i.e. (reflexively) to sit up
[ἀναίτιος] from {{g1}} (as a negative particle) and {{g159}} (in the sense of {{g156}}); innocent
[ἀνασταυρόω] from {{g303}} and {{g4717}}; to recrucify (figuratively)
[ἀναστενάζω] from {{g303}} and {{g4727}}; to sigh deeply
[ἀναρίθμητος] from {{g1}} (as a negative particle) and a derivative of {{g705}}; unnumbered, i.e. without number
[ἀνασείω] from {{g303}} and {{g4579}}; figuratively, to excite
[ἀναπτύσσω] from {{g303}} (in the sense of reversal) and {{g4428}}; to unroll (a scroll or volume)
[ἀνάπτω] from {{g303}} and {{g681}}; to enkindle

[ἀνάστασις] from {{g450}}; a standing up again, i.e. (literally) a resurrection from death (individual, genitive case or by implication, (its author)), or (figuratively) a (moral) recovery (of spiritual truth)
[ἀναστατόω] from a derivative of {{g450}} (in the sense of removal); properly, to drive out of home, i.e. (by implication) to disturb (literally or figuratively)
[ἀνασκευάζω] from {{g303}} (in the sense of reversal) and a derivative of {{g4632}}; properly, to pack up (baggage), i.e. (by implication, and figuratively) to upset
[ἀνασπάω] from {{g303}} and {{g4685}}; to take up or extricate
[ἄν] a primary particle, denoting a supposition, wish, possibility or uncertainty Usually unexpressed except by the subjunctive or potential mood. Also contracted for {{g1437}}.

[ἀνά] a primary preposition and adverb; properly, up; but (by extension) used (distributively) severally, or (locally) at (etc.) In compounds (as a prefix) it often means (by implication) repetition, intensity, reversal, etc.
[Ἀμώς] of Hebrew origin ({{h531}}); Amos, an Israelite
[ἀναβάλλομαι] middle voice from {{g303}} and {{g906}}; to put off (for oneself)
[ἀναβιβάζω] from {{g303}} and a derivative of the base of {{g939}}; to cause to go up, i.e. haul (a net)
[ἀναβαθμός] from {{g305}} (compare {{g898}}); a stairway
[ἀναβαίνω] from {{g303}} and the base of {{g939}}; to go up (literally or figuratively)
[ἀναβλέπω] from {{g303}} and {{g991}}; to look up; by implication, to recover sight
[ἀνάβλεψις] from {{g308}}; restoration of sight
[ἀναγνωρίζομαι] middle voice from {{g303}} and {{g1107}}; to make (oneself) known
[ἀνάγκη] from {{g303}} and the base of {{g43}}; constraint (literally or figuratively); by implication, distress
[ἀναγκάζω] from {{g318}}; to necessitate
[ἀναγινώσκω] from {{g303}} and {{g1097}}; to know again, i.e. (by extension) to read
[ἀναγκαστῶς] adverb from a derivative of {{g315}}; compulsorily
[ἀναγκαῖος] from {{g318}}; necessary; by implication, close (of kin)
[ἀναβολή] from {{g306}}; a putting off
[ἀναβοάω] from {{g303}} and {{g994}}; to halloo
[ἀναγεννάω] from {{g303}} and {{g1080}}; to beget or (by extension) bear (again)
[ἀναγγέλλω] from {{g303}} and the base of {{g32}}; to announce (in detail)
